{"tid":855220,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"湯家驊大讚施政報告「歷史性」：一反歷屆政府小修小補心態","createTime":"2018-10-10T02:33:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T06:51:41.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":70,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"4b37822bd9ce564ce6fb4c267dcb8d5c10f97605","tid":855220,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T02:33:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/tom-03_su3XH_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Ftom-03_su3XH_1200x0.png&h=ed60b87c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥將於今早11時發表任內第二份《施政報告》。身兼行會成員的民主思路召集人湯家驊，今早在施政報告正式發表前已大讚報告是「歷史性」，有別於歷屆政府小修小補的心態。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊在今早7時許於FB發文，形容今次是一份歷史性的《施政報告》，「一反過往回歸之來歷屆政府那種以左顧右盼、小修小補之心態所寫出的政策報告，這是一份充滿管治信心、彰顯共同希望的報告」。<br />\n<br />\n他又指這是一份理念性報告，與過往歷屆特首不同，從現屆政府的管治理念出發，在各項具爭議性課題作出決定性處理政策的報告。他形容大家不應期望一份《施政報告》可以解決所有深層次、特別是政治問題，「但這一份刻劃了未來二、三十年的宏觀發展藍圖的報告；希望香港人能齊心努力，以包容忍耐之心，令香港再現光芒！」<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥將於今日早上11時到立法會發表施政報告；於下午2時許再舉行記者會，就《施政報告》回答傳媒提問；晚上7時她將會出席電視論壇。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/先興奮-湯家驊大讚施政報告-歷史性-一反歷屆政府小修小補心態/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%85%88%E8%88%88%E5%A5%AE-%E6%B9%AF%E5%AE%B6%E9%A9%8A%E5%A4%A7%E8%AE%9A%E6%96%BD%E6%94%BF%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A-%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E6%80%A7-%E4%B8%80%E5%8F%8D%E6%AD%B7%E5%B1%86%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%B0%8F%E4%BF%AE%E5%B0%8F%E8%A3%9C%E5%BF%83%E6%85%8B%2F&d=vWSirjpo6HHfdCpzl4aijm6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=27c40bc2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%85%88%E8%88%88%E5%A5%AE-%E6%B9%AF%E5%AE%B6%E9%A9%8A%E5%A4%A7%E8%AE%9A%E6%96%BD%E6%94%BF%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A-%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E6%80%A7-%E4%B8%80%E5%8F%8D%E6%AD%B7%E5%B1%86%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%B0%8F%E4%BF%AE%E5%B0%8F%E8%A3%9C%E5%BF%83%E6%85%8B%2F&h=c6269120\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/先興奮-湯家驊大讚施政報告-歷史性-一反歷屆政府小修小補心態/</a>"},{"pid":"cd59256d9245ec1e6aa0fcb30c6b91705288125f","tid":855220,"uid":37757,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T02:35:07.000Z","msg":"歷史性垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce17fd86c272722d4d3b8b4e98e7434842807a44","tid":855220,"uid":50984,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T02:39:22.000Z","msg":"咁十一哥嘅「性歷史」又點樣呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e0cb0320478ad5d532c34f68e2245f5e405ddad","tid":855220,"uid":141151,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"cd59256d9245ec1e6aa0fcb30c6b91705288125f","tid":855220,"uid":37757,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T02:35:07.000Z","msg":"歷史性垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T02:40:50.000Z","msg":"好有雪廠feel<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de9fb5823a862f4c3e40899f1970bac8567505b3","tid":855220,"uid":151389,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T02:42:49.000Z","msg":"親共媒體都算<br />\n點解啲所謂民主派媒體咁撚鐘意訪問十一哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇人想知佢意見 除非有雪廠街絕密資料"},{"pid":"45dae2cdc054f5a0be37fc3484c6099c440e5c0d","tid":855220,"uid":26329,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0e0cb0320478ad5d532c34f68e2245f5e405ddad","tid":855220,"uid":141151,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"cd59256d9245ec1e6aa0fcb30c6b91705288125f","tid":855220,"uid":37757,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T02:35:07.000Z","msg":"歷史性垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T02:40:50.000Z","msg":"好有雪廠feel<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T03:03:19.000Z","msg":"已經係歷史文件 不具任何效力"},{"pid":"fda23c0fd690011e